  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s1",
      "text": "It was just before 2:30 pm in my hometown, Wenchuan.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p1",
      "tr": "那是在我的家乡汶川，下午2:30之前。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "It指代时间。just before意为“就在...之前”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/aMKBbBUvgmGsZMPUQiBFoC.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s2",
      "text": "I was having a music lesson at school.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p1",
      "tr": "我当时正在学校上音乐课。",
      "g": "过去进行时",
      "d": "was having表示过去某个时刻正在进行的动作。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/S5CP5CnfY6eHuRNEp26rig.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s3",
      "text": "Suddenly, the ground shook hard and I was thrown to the floor.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p1",
      "tr": "突然，地面剧烈摇晃，我被摔到了地板上。",
      "g": "并列复合句",
      "d": "shook是shake的过去式。was thrown是被动语态。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/UQKNHjDfNza437QWR6ymEE.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s4",
      "text": "People were shouting all around me.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p1",
      "tr": "周围的人都在尖叫。",
      "g": "过去进行时",
      "d": "all around me意为“在我周围”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/JTZW8EofDdhPYzfYH4tNJD.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s5",
      "text": "I jumped to my feet and rushed outside.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p1",
      "tr": "我一跃而起，冲向室外。",
      "g": "并列谓语",
      "d": "jump to one's feet意为“跳起来，一跃而起”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/cwzhBYFk6kdMg2p6eoCun6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s6",
      "text": "I was shocked to find all the other buildings were reduced to pieces.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p1",
      "tr": "我震惊地发现所有其他的建筑都变成了碎片。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语 + 不定式",
      "d": "be shocked to do sth. 震惊地做某事。reduce to pieces 变成碎片。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/jTbZXJ3mAxfhXTbez7HysU.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s7",
      "text": "I was shaking all over with fear.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p1",
      "tr": "我全身因恐惧而发抖。",
      "g": "过去进行时",
      "d": "shake all over 全身发抖。with fear 因为恐惧。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/dDYebmPnXGH7jufdgM8WWG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s8",
      "text": "Then, a pair of strong hands reached out to me – I was saved.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p1",
      "tr": "这时，一双有力的大手伸向了我——我获救了。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 状语",
      "d": "reach out to 伸向。was saved 被动语态。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/p5w2gyLo7xiqaoRqZXZJTM.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s9",
      "text": "I can never forget those soldiers, firemen, doctors and nurses.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p2",
      "tr": "我永远忘不了那些士兵、消防员、医生和护士。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "can never forget 永远忘不了。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/TPqnyidka3T3efpTzt3vGW.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s10",
      "text": "Day and night, they raced against time to save as many people as possible.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p2",
      "tr": "他们日以继夜地与时间赛跑，尽可能多地救人。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 目的状语",
      "d": "race against time 与时间赛跑。as...as possible 尽可能...。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/fy5V3jFvsnUN9mTqRFLS97.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s11",
      "text": "I was deeply touched by their courage and hard work.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p2",
      "tr": "我被他们的勇气和努力深深打动了。",
      "g": "被动语态",
      "d": "be touched by 被...打动。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/N6T6PKkoe76dkFkb9SDirD.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s12",
      "text": "So I made up my mind to become one of them.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p2",
      "tr": "所以我下定决心要成为他们中的一员。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "make up one's mind 下定决心。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/XCi37e763dPQL8HJhpUZ32.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s13",
      "text": "And I did! I graduated from college and became a nurse.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p2",
      "tr": "我做到了！我大学毕业后成为了一名护士。",
      "g": "并列谓语",
      "d": "graduate from 从...毕业。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ZUnokRdcPZUS7GWMLcjiLZ.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s14",
      "text": "One day, I heard another hospital needed support.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p3",
      "tr": "有一天，我听说另一家医院需要支援。",
      "g": "宾语从句",
      "d": "heard后面省略了that引导的宾语从句。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/mHmn2vAUhHvjPySFmaCVBZ.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s15",
      "text": "Right away, I signed up to help.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p3",
      "tr": "我立刻报名去帮忙。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 目的状语",
      "d": "right away 立刻。sign up 报名。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/FunNG6CZbU3cB3CeVDV9qh.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s16",
      "text": "I still remembered the warmth of those helping hands 12 years ago.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p3",
      "tr": "我仍然记得12年前那些援助之手的温暖。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "warmth 是 warm 的名词形式。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/7vLCTBZNH3eBEqK6fM8LAQ.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s17",
      "text": "It was time for me to offer mine.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p3",
      "tr": "轮到我伸出援手了。",
      "g": "It is time for sb. to do 句型",
      "d": "mine指代my helping hands。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/T4DnWBLSaNtDgERA92oCYR.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s18",
      "text": "The work was by no means easy.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p4",
      "tr": "这项工作绝非易事。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "by no means 绝不，一点也不。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/5Z6k82dFite5mGuzpXHb2A.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s19",
      "text": "The head nurse, Ye Man, gave me a lot of help.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p4",
      "tr": "护士长叶曼给了我很多帮助。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 间接宾语 + 直接宾语",
      "d": "Ye Man是The head nurse的同位语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/oa6xiRZJrDPVTe7e7FA54d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s20",
      "text": "For me, she was a patient teacher and a kind friend.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p4",
      "tr": "对我来说，她是一位耐心的老师，也是一位善良的朋友。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "patient 既可以做名词“病人”，也可以做形容词“耐心的”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/UwFGnoQDnH7xKQ2T4WjPkj.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s21",
      "text": "However, this wasn't the beginning of our connection.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p4",
      "tr": "然而，这并不是我们联系的开始。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "不是。它是 was not 的缩写形式",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/udXTvMfr2Xn8u7Fs9W8sY4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s22",
      "text": "She had offered a helping hand to Wenchuan 12 years ago.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p4",
      "tr": "12年前，她曾向汶川伸出过援助之手。",
      "g": "过去完成时",
      "d": "had offered 表示在过去（12年前）已经发生的动作。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/mWFvatL7acr7zYmmRq5MfX.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s23",
      "text": "Can you imagine my surprise?",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p4",
      "tr": "你能想象我的惊讶吗？",
      "g": "疑问句",
      "d": "imagine 想象。surprise 惊讶。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/DYmy4nKABZCGYEwjHKGEj2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s24",
      "text": "At that time she was my age, and also a new nurse, just like me!",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p4",
      "tr": "那时她和我现在的年纪一样大，也是一名新护士，就像我一样！",
      "g": "并列复合句",
      "d": "my age 意为“我的年纪”。just like 就像。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/6VVaiMES6QXgixwMLWdAQe.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s25",
      "text": "Even today, I still feel lucky to have had such an amazing experience in life.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p5",
      "tr": "即使在今天，我仍然觉得在生命中拥有这样一段奇妙的经历是很幸运的。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语 + 不定式",
      "d": "feel lucky to do 觉得做某事很幸运。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/xjmr8hyi4tqWL5VUXHtC8Y.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "g8b-u4-p2-s26",
      "text": "Love leads to love, and so creates a circle of goodwill and kindness.",
      "paragraphId": "g8b-u4-p2-p5",
      "tr": "爱引发爱，从而创造了一个善意和仁慈的循环。",
      "g": "并列复合句",
      "d": "lead to 导致，引发。goodwill 善意。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ta8B5Z53SHLLgiRHn9uPaN.mp3"
    }
  ],
