        "C. It was time for her to find a new job in the hospital",
        "D. It was time for her to return to her hometown Wenchuan"
      ],
      "answer": "B. It was time for her to help others as she was helped",
      "rationaleZh": "文中'mine'指代'helping hands'，作者认为现在轮到自己像当年被救助一样去帮助别人了。"
